Needed modules:

python:
    2.6 or 2.7

wxPython:
    python-wxgtk2.8
    python-wxtools
    python-wxversion

modbus-tk :
    apt-get install python-setuptools
    python setup.py install (from modbus-tk folder, download from http://code.google.com/p/modbus-tk/downloads/list)

PyEphem:
    apt-get install python-dev
    easy_install pyephem

Numpy:
    apt-get install python-pip
    pip install numpy

MySQL db:
    apt-get install
    apt-get install python-mysqldb
    
Database scheme can be found in db package: db_init.sql
    mysql -u root -p <db_init.sql
